00:00:07.863 --> 00:00:09.592
Welcome on kitchenbooktv channel

00:00:09.861 --> 00:00:10.922
I would like to show you a recipe for mayonnaise

00:00:11.424 --> 00:00:14.635
two organic eggs were two minutes in hot water

00:00:19.507 --> 00:00:21.831
separate the eggs

00:00:28.005 --> 00:00:32.713
add two egg yolks to the bowl

00:00:39.088 --> 00:00:43.809
add a teaspoon of mustard

00:00:45.306 --> 00:00:52.117
add two teaspoons of vinegar

00:00:52.377 --> 00:00:54.494
mix

00:00:55.275 --> 00:01:08.268
add 250 ml very slow stream of oil and
mixed in the same direction

00:01:23.214 --> 00:01:46.298
spice with salt, white pepper, lemon juice, sugar

00:01:46.298 --> 00:01:48.268
Enjoy

00:01:49.463 --> 00:01:56.434
the eggs and oil should be room temperature

